Kusalattika
Pañhāvāra
Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Navippayuttaduka
Catukka
1770Navippayuttapaccayā nahetupaccayā naārammaṇapaccayā adhipatiyā tīṇi, anantare satta, samanantare satta, sahajāte tīṇi, aññamaññe tīṇi, nissaye tīṇi, upanissaye nava, āsevane tīṇi, kamme pañca, vipāke ekaṃ, āhāre tīṇi, indriye tīṇi, jhāne tīṇi, magge tīṇi, sampayutte tīṇi, atthiyā tīṇi, natthiyā satta, vigate satta, avigate tīṇi…pe… .
